  "title": "Project Coordinator",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>responsible for technical drawings, project schedule</li>\n  <li>to coordinate works on/off site;</li>\n  <li>to liaise closely with clients and designers with proper documentation</li>\n  <li>to plan and work closely with team members and production team to ensure timely delivery and completion of projects</li>\n  <li>to monitor projects with progress reports and submit to client</li>\n  <li>to carry out inspection of materials/products delivered on site</li>\n  <li>to prepare site for proper handover for client to sign and takeover site</li>\n  <li>ad-hoc duties assigned, if any</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>technical skill in furniture construction will be preferred</li>\n  <li>experience in A&amp;A works under commercial and hospitality sector is preferred</li>\n  <li>self-motivated and good working attitude</li>\n  <li>able to work independently as well as a good team player</li>\n  <li>strong problem-solving and follow-up skill</li>\n</ul>",
